# SUPERNOVA MOTORS INC. - APEX BATTERIES SUPPLY AGREEMENT
**Execution Date:** January 1, 2024  
**Parties:** Supernova Motors Inc. ("Buyer") & Apex Batteries LLC ("Vendor")  

## 1. Supply  
Vendor supplies 10,000 lithium cells annually at $150/unit (Exhibit A). Delivery FOB Austin.  

## 2. Term & Termination  
Initial 2 years; auto-renew. Termination: Buyer 90 days' notice; Vendor 30 days for non-payment. No last-time buy.  

## 3. Indemnity  
Vendor indemnifies for defects only (direct damages, cap $500K). No IP or cyber coverage.  

## 4. IP  
Buyer gets non-exclusive license; no assignment of improvements.  

